      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;app-architecture&#34;&gt;App Architecture&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/software-architecture.png&#34; alt=&#34;App Architecture&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;overview&#34;&gt;Overview&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;We will grab all our movie data in the &lt;a href=&#34;https://developer.themoviedb.org/docs/getting-started&#34;&gt;Tmdb API&lt;/a&gt;. The API already offers login and this means users has the ability to add, remove, update, and rate movies.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;app-design-pattern-mvvm&#34;&gt;App Design Pattern (MVVM)&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://journaldev.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/2018/04/android-mvvm-pattern.png&#34; alt=&#34;MVVM&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;We are going to use MVVM Design pattern to make it easier for collaborations, scalable, and testing.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;I will create another tutorial file on how everything works with the codebase&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
